channel.title: Syntrix, Need testers
channel.description:
[center]Hello,
I am working on my server "Syntrix", it has pretty much perfect combat,everything redone and stuff but just need to work on a few things to make it perfect for release.
I am looking for a good developer who can add perfect summoning with specials .
If the server is ready to launch I will be investing over 500 usd in promotionals & banners . Also planning to pay the developer good with monthly payments.
Contact me with skype or a pm on here . Skype: Rafr200[/center]
